@startuml Manage_Equipment_State_Diagram
title Manage Equipment - State Diagram
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Available : Create equipment

Available --> Broken : Issue is reported
Broken --> Maintenance : Issue is being handled
Maintenance --> Available : Issue resolved or maintenance completed

Available --> Maintenance : Set under maintenance
Maintenance --> Broken : Serious issue found
Broken --> Available : Mark as available

Available --> Deleted : Delete equipment
Maintenance --> Deleted : Delete equipment
Broken --> Deleted : Delete equipment

Deleted --> [*]

@enduml
